Log in AWS account fro aws.amazon.com


Go to Services/Developer Tools/CodeBuild. At could create new builder.

Create builder name disec and Soucre provider from gitHub.

Go to S3 to create new Bucket for this builder output.

Gt to Devloper Toolss


Git EC2 running and git project from git hub repoistory

 

1. Prepare a project codes - java + c++.
2. Prepare EC2 instances - install Cdoe Deploy Agent & Tags
3. Create Code Deploy IAM Service Role
4. Create EC2 Instance Profile.
5. Create Code Deploy Application & Deployment Group.
6. Crate Code Pipeline.


                                   
                                   
